# Privacy Policy

## Introduction

This Privacy Policy describes how user data is collected, used, and protected when interacting with our video game. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal data.

## Data Collection

We may collect the following types of data:
- Information about your device, including the unique device identifier and platform details.
- Information about your use of the app, such as gameplay progress, achievements, and in-game purchases.

We do not collect or process sensitive personal data, such as your name, address, or payment information, except when provided through third-party platforms (e.g., app stores).

## In-Game Purchases

All in-game purchases are virtual and intended solely for use within the game. Please note that upon deleting or reinstalling the game, any purchased items or currency may be lost. We cannot restore purchases lost as a result of deleting the game.

## Use of Data

We use the collected data for:
- Improving the gameplay experience;
- Analyzing interactions with the game to optimize performance and develop new features;
- Internal reporting and analytics.

We do not share your data with third parties without your consent, except as required by law.

## Data Retention

We retain your data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy. Upon discontinuing use of the game or deleting your account, your data will be removed.

## Data Security

We take all necessary measures to protect your data from unauthorized access and use. However, no method of data transmission over the internet is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute data security.

## Changes to the Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the date of the latest update.

## Contact Information

If you have any questions about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at: usus9027@gmail.com.

